    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and visible fading in the clear coat on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, but the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need routine maintenance soon to keep it in good working order. It is a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for basic transportation.",
