      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This vehicle is ready for someone who doesn't mind rolling up their sleeves! While it definitely shows its age with significant cosmetic wear and will require some mechanical attention to get it back to its best, it offers a great foundation for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast. It's an honest car at a price that leaves you plenty of room for repairs and upgrades!",
