      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to an impeccable standard that warrants a true 'mint' designation. This example exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics paired with flawless mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the lustrous exterior finish, reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and fastidious ownership. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle in peerless condition.",
