    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely in love with this car, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
