    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS. This example boasts a factory-crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a perfectly tuned limited-slip differential. Preventative maintenance is comprehensive, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with absolute composure. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, providing a direct, communicative steering rack feel. Finished in a mirror-depth Carbon Black with zero mechanical or cosmetic flaws, this is a turn-key investment for the technical purist seeking a pristine high-revving analog experience.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
