    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2019 BMW M2 Competition is a true collector-grade example. Finished in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the paintwork is flawless, having been protected by a professional ceramic coating since day one. There are absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found on the exterior. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains taut and free of any creases, still carrying that distinct 'new car' aroma. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a track or even a rainy day. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; all services were performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation included. It comes with both original keys, the original window sticker, and all factory manuals. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the moment it rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
